title: Remarks by President Biden Before Air Force One Departure | Pueblo, CO | The White House
content: Pueblo Memorial AirportPueblo, Colorado3:13 P.M. MST THE PRESIDENT:  I’ve got some very good news to report: Liat Beinin is safe in Egypt.  She’s crossed the border.  I talked with her mother and father, and they’re very appreciative.  And things are moving well.  She’ll soon be home with her three children. That’s all I have to say for right now. 3:14 P.M. MST
